    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Card games played with tarot cards, especially the central European game played with 22 Greater Arcana tarot cards and up to 56 regular modern playing cards.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
